    "name": "Chunk 2/2",
    "doc_id": "edc0aa58c25a485a9c05c12750ec21aa",
    "text": "IBM worked on the design and deployment of a formalized, end-to-end workflow and case management solution that replaced the current manual, spreadsheet-based processes. This new system enabled real-time tracking, operational control, and governance of remediation activities, while supporting multiple outreach and data enrichment channels such as third-party services and relationship managers.  \nThe Business is now empowered to make timely, risk-informed decisions to retain, block, or exit customers based on their financial crime risk profile.   This also improved operational efficiency, data integrity, and strategic decision-making across the Business Savings portfolio.  \nResults:  \n- Replacement of manual process by end-to-end workflow and case management told reduce manual errors and increased operational efficiency\n- Enhanced Regulatory Compliance and reduced exposure to financial crime\n- Strategic decision making across the Business Savings portfolio",
